00:30:16.950 --> 00:30:19.760
and interviews in America, sort
of background interviews some

00:30:19.760 --> 00:30:22.850
of them did appear
actually for the film.

00:30:22.850 --> 00:30:26.910 position:56%
And as often happens, similar story,

00:30:26.910 --> 00:30:30.140
in the course of my research
I heard someone sort of --

00:30:30.140 --> 00:30:33.550
, I think it was a historian
who said oh I heard this thing

00:30:33.550 --> 00:30:36.730
with 700 photographs were found
in a suitcase on the street

00:30:36.730 --> 00:30:39.650
in Massachusetts and you know
I don't really know about it

00:30:39.650 --> 00:30:41.840
