00:36:07.960 --> 00:36:11.040
So during those autumn months the
members of the division would fan

00:36:11.040 --> 00:36:14.680
out across the city every
day to trace the blast paths,

00:36:14.680 --> 00:36:18.260
calibrate the bomb damage and
analyze the physical destruction

00:36:18.260 --> 00:36:21.790
of the city and it was is you
could imagine really tough going.

00:36:21.790 --> 00:36:24.670
