actually was one of the members

00:36:32.350 --> 00:36:34.000
and he wrote the cities of Japan

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:40.440
in those dark autumn days was a
manifestation of unspeakable gloom,

00:36:40.440 --> 00:36:45.050
only ashes and gaunt,
freestanding chimneys remained.

00:36:45.050 --> 00:36:48.390
So in order to document the
damage, to identify, catalog

00:36:48.390 --> 00:36:52.280
