draped over a lounge chair.

00:43:07.510 --> 00:43:09.900
He was trying to get
out of a side door.

00:43:09.900 --> 00:43:14.820
He was close, about 15 feet
away, but he didn't make it.

00:43:14.820 --> 00:43:18.610
According to the Times, Corsbee
