00:43:18.610 --> 00:43:19.910
a necktie.

00:43:19.910 --> 00:43:23.130
Because of the intense heat the
firemen had to suspend their search

00:43:23.130 --> 00:43:26.240
and rescue and when they
resumed they found Robert junior

00:43:26.240 --> 00:43:29.640
in his pajamas in an upstairs
bathtub full of water.

00:43:29.640 --> 00:43:33.410
He was probably trying to keep away
from the flames said Apostalico

00:43:33.410 --> 00:43:36.420 position:56%
and he had died of smoke inhalation.

00:43:36.420 --> 00:43:40.930
So the Corsbees had thrown a party
the night before which according

00:43:40.930 --> 00:43:43.280
to witnesses they had
candles burning.

00:43:43.280 --> 00:43:46.320
After everyone had gone home
they probably had a nightcap

00:43:46.320 --> 00:43:49.030
on their living room
sofa and dozed off.

00:43:49.030 --> 00:43:51.250
The candles in the living
room must have tipped

00:43:51.250 --> 00:43:55.580
